take more than an hour.

502
00:20:48,583 --> 00:20:49,583
Yes, of course.

503
00:20:49,666 --> 00:20:52,750
There's something else.

504
00:20:52,833 --> 00:20:55,375
Gus planned a special
surprise for you.

505
00:20:57,291 --> 00:20:58,250
What's all this?

506
